      "english": "{2:Reining in} {1:all} {0:of them}, {5:having effected} {3:the reining in}, {4:the bringing under control}, {6:yoked}, {7:composed}, {8:being so}, {9:let him sit} {10:‘intent on Me’} — {11:‘I}, {12:Vāsudeva}, {13:the inmost Self of all}, {14:am the Supreme} {15:of whom}: {16:he} is {17:‘intent on Me’}, {20:‘I am} {18:no} {19:other} {21:than That}’ — {23:so let him sit}, {24:that is} {25:the meaning}. {26:Thus} for such {27:a seated} {28:ascetic}, {31:he in whose} {29:control} {30:indeed} {32:the senses} {33:abide} {34:by the force of practice}, {35:his} {36:prajñā} {37:stands firm}.",
