      "english": "He {2:elaborates} {0:that very thing} {3:by ‘vihāya’}. {8:Giving up} {5:kāmas}, {6:objects}, {7:with freedom from longing}, {9:he who} {10:‘moves’} {11:— eats}; {16:and} {15:is devoid of ahaṅkāra and mineness} {12:‘I eat’} {14:and the like} — {17:he} {18:indeed} {19:is the (true) man}; {20:he} {21:alone} {23:attains} {22:liberation}, {25:that is the meaning}.",
